{"tid":613384,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)隔世救未來 環太平洋1-2","createTime":"2018-04-01T15:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T19:19:28.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"46dd6de6b6797de014b077548e5b9fe9718f52e5","tid":613384,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=57e53187\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c1da7c1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZtPselh0ugY/Tqd9w9-zczI/AAAAAAAADgo/GDwH92TEP_w/s400/Frequency+2000+Hollywood+Movie+Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZtPselh0ugY%2FTqd9w9-zczI%2FAAAAAAAADgo%2FGDwH92TEP_w%2Fs400%2FFrequency%2B2000%2BHollywood%2BMovie%2BPoster.jpg&h=314d5fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/f3/Pacific_Rim_FilmPoster.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Ff%2Ff3%2FPacific_Rim_FilmPoster.jpeg&h=959860fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/03/Pacific_Rim_Uprising_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F03%2FPacific_Rim_Uprising_Poster.jpg&h=03b707d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1969年的10月12日，約翰的父親在布朗區的救災裏死去，而那場悲劇使得他的生活與成長過程中，皆蒙上一層無法擺脫的陰影。然而，事情經過三十年後，某天夜晚約翰意外地找到他父親生前所用的無線電，並在隨興的使用撥接之下，突然跟一位陌生男子搭上線。而且，無線電在沒有插電源的情況下，卻能依舊正常通話，更讓約翰意想不到的是，與他隔空對話的不是別人，正是他三十年前還在人世的父親..<br />\n<br />\n2.2013年，太平洋深處出現一個稱為「突破點」的平行宇宙傳送門，為一大群外星巨獸「怪獸」（Kaiju）展開一條侵略的道路。接二連三的怪獸襲擊造成人類傷亡和損失均慘重，預測災難會永無止境後，世界合作研發了能夠和怪獸抗衡的武器「機甲獵人」（Jaeger）：對抗怪獸的巨大機器人，由兩名腦部神經網路互相串連（浮動神經元連結）的操縱者同步操作。靠著機甲獵人，人類開始抗擊怪獸勢力，為長達數年的怪獸戰役拉開了序幕。於2020年，美國機甲「吉普賽危機」負責攔截一隻即將登上阿拉斯加的怪獸「鬼刀頭」時，但操縱機甲的萊利與楊希&middot;貝克特兄弟爲了救一艘漁船，便違反命令來到深海區作戰。楊希被怪獸直接扯出駕駛艙而陣亡，萊利單獨操縱受損的機甲而最終獲勝，由於受到兄弟陣亡的陰影所折磨，決定放棄保家衛國的使命<br />\n<br />\n3.故事背景設定於突破點之戰的10年後，人類用以戰勝外星巨獸「怪獸」（Kaiju）[註 2]的巨型武裝機器人「機甲獵人」（Jaeger）[註 3]已成為了人類史上最強大的全球防禦力量。當怪獸的威脅再度降臨時，機甲獵人計畫注入了年輕的新血，以對抗強大的怪獸勢力<br />\n<br />\n12 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> *太平洋2係薯片版,好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b2347c8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=040d0636\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdae1f4e36878437d4925f0ec8bb25feab175f64","tid":613384,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s